title: In Another World, I'm Called the Black Healer
description: One day, 22-year-old Kanzaki Misuzu is suddenly transported to another world. Status screens, magic, doesn't this seem RPG-like?! Shrewdly making use of game knowledge accumulated from her life as an otaku and adapting it in a world with magic, she becomes known as the "Black Healer," before she knows it?
